ABOUT
======

Rockon is a XMMS2 client based on EFL libraries.

DEPENDENCIES
============

 * XMMS2 (0.6 DrMattDestruction) http://wiki.xmms2.xmms.se
   - with support for xmms2-client-ecore
 * EFL http://www.enlightenment.org
   - Ecore
   - Edje
   - Elementary

INSTALL
=======

Rockon uses the Waf build system.
Just run:
$ ./waf configure build

If successful the executable will be at: build/default/src/rockon

DEBUG OUTPUT
============

If you want debug messages printed on terminal you must set some environment variables, all necessary variables are in the file eina_env_vars.
